title: Wednesday Post Show (02-23-22)
itunes:title: Wednesday Post Show (02-23-22)
description:
A caller has a question about Eddie and his wife and if he gives her time for herself to get away from the kids. Another caller has a question if Bobby is still playing his Oculus. Bobby reads new stories he didn’t get to in the radio show including what happened when a college student tried to make rocket fuel and child who was left in a daycare. Scuba Steve also shares a story of a mysterious sight he saw in Hawaii.
